Title: Inception
Description: A thief who steals corporate secrets through use of dream-sharing technology.

Title: The Matrix
Description: A computer hacker learns from mysterious rebels about the false nature of his reality.

Title: Interstellar
Description: A team of explorers travel through a wormhole in space in an attempt to ensure humanity's survival.

Title: Pulp Fiction
Description: The lives of two mob hitmen, a boxer, and others intertwine in tales of violence and redemption.

Title: The Shawshank Redemption
Description: Two imprisoned men bond over a number of years, finding solace and eventual redemption.

Title: The Godfather
Description: An organized crime dynasty's aging patriarch transfers control of his empire to his reluctant son.

Title: Fight Club
Description: An insomniac office worker and a soapmaker form an underground fight club.

Title: Forrest Gump
Description: The presidencies of Kennedy and Johnson, Vietnam, and more through the eyes of Forrest Gump.

Title: The Dark Knight
Description: Batman must accept one of the greatest psychological and physical tests of his ability to fight injustice.
